Package administration

Class StorageController

  • java.lang.Object
    • administration.StorageController

  • public class StorageController
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Max. The StorageController class is creating all the Daos, retrieving them from the DataController. The StorageController is the contact point for all database-related actions from the rest of the program. Whenever something needs to be inserted, deleted or updated in the database the methods of this class are called.
